@hostname=localhost
@port=5042
@token=token

### Anonymous endpoint
GET http://{{hostname}}:{{port}}

### Register
POST http://{{hostname}}:{{port}}/identity/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "Email": "example@example.com",
  "Password": "[PLACEHOLDER]-1a"
}

### Login (Bearer token)
POST http://{{hostname}}:{{port}}/identity/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "Email": "example@example.com",
  "Password": "[PLACEHOLDER]-1a"
}

### Authenticated endpoint
GET http://{{hostname}}:{{port}}/requires-auth

### Authenticated endpoint (Bearer token)
GET http://{{hostname}}:{{port}}/requires-auth
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Info
GET http://{{hostname}}:{{port}}/identity/manage/info
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

