Content-Type: application/json

{
}

### Enable 2fa
POST http://{{hostname}}:{{port}}/identity/manage/2fa
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "Enable": true,
  "TwoFactorCode": "45375"
}

